criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  obese (BMI ≥ 35)

          -  aged ≥18 years

          -  willing to participate in the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  inability to provide informed consent to participate in the study (i.e. psychotic or
             mentally impaired patients);

          -  insufficient knowledge of Italian;

          -  presence of a medical condition associated with weight loss or gain;

          -  major psychiatric illness and cognitive deficit;

          -  participation in another weight-loss program or psychological intervention;

          -  use of medication known to affect weight;

          -  participants in an individual or group psycho-therapeutic program;

          -  history of weight loss surgery or weight loss surgery scheduled within the next year;

          -  being pregnant or intended pregnancy within the year.
